<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= espanol ? "es":"en" %>">
<head>
  <title><%= espanol ? "Sobre Nosotros":"About the Project"%></title>
  <meta property="og:title" content="<%= espanol ? "Sobre Nosotros":"About the Project"%>" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="" />

  <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
</head>

<body id="about-body">
    <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>


    <div id="title-box" class="center-wrapper about-title">
      <div class="about change-bg" id="inner-title-box">
        <h1><%= espanol ? "Sobre Nosotros":"About the Project"%></h1>
      </div>
    </div>

<section id="about-intro-text" class="container max-width">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">

  <div class="about">

	<% if (espanol) { %>
    <p>Somos un grupo de alumnos de camarógrafos, diseñadores y desarrolladores web, periodistas y facultad unido por un objetivo común: compartir las voces de la juventud de Cuba.</p>

    <p>Somos parte de un proyecto anual de La Escuela de los Medios de Comunicación y Periodismo de UNC-Chapel Hill. En los proyectos pasados, alumnos han reportado en cinco continentes y han producido trabajo premiado. Como estudiantes, estamos aprendiendo los beneficios y desafíos de reportar sobre culturas distintas; como periodistas, estamos trabajando juntos a contar las historias que moldean el mundo.</p>

  	<% } else { %>
      <p>We are a group of student videographers, web designers and developers, reporters and faculty brought together by a common goal: to paint an honest portrait of Puerto Rico in the wake of Hurricane Maria, and looking toward future storms.</p>
      <p>We are a part of an annual project by UNC-Chapel Hill’s School of Media and Journalism. In past projects, students have reported across five continents and produced award-winning multimedia work. As students, we’re learning the rewards and challenges of reporting on different cultures; as journalists, we are working as a team to tell the stories that are shaping the globe.</p>
    <% } %>
	</div>


</div><!-- end row-->

</section> <!--end container -->

  <div class="team-nav">
    <ul>
      <li data-filter="all" class="active everyone about-nav"><%= espanol ? "Todos":"Everyone"%></li>
      <li data-filter=".vid" class="videographer about-nav"><%= espanol ? "Videógrafa/o":"Videographer"%></li>
      <li data-filter=".rep" class="reporter about-nav"><%= espanol ? "Periodista":"Reporter"%></li>
      <li data-filter=".des" class="designdev about-nav"><%= espanol ? "Diseñadora":"Designer"%></li>
      <li data-filter=".dev" class="designdev about-nav"><%= espanol ? "Desarrollador/a":"Developer"%></li>
      <li data-filter=".coach" class="coaches about-nav"><%= espanol ? "Instructor":"Coach"%></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <p class="mobile-only-text">Tap on a photo to learn more about each team member.</p>

  <!-- fa-github,  -->

  <div class="container">
  <div class="row" id="team-photos">

    <% for (i in team) {  %>
        <div class="mix col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-xl-4 <%=team[i]["roleid"] %>">
          <div class="team-image-box">
            <p class="bio">
              <%= espanol ? team[i]["biospanish"]:team[i]["bio"] %> </p>
            <img alt="<%=team[i]["fullname"]%>" src="/assets/images/team/edited/<%=team[i]["firstname"]%>.jpg">
          </div>
          <div class="team-info">
            <p class="role"><%=espanol ? team[i]["rolespanish"]:team[i]["role"] %></p>
            <p class="team-name"><%=team[i]["fullname"]%> </p>
            <% if ( team[i]["portfolio"]){ %>
            <p class="portfolio">
              <a href="<%=team[i]["portfolio"]%>" target="_blank"><%= espanol ? "Portfolio":"Portfolio" %></a>
            </p>
            <% if (team[i]["portfolio"] && team[i]["social"]){ %>
            <span> | </span>
            <% } %>
            <% } else { }%>
            <% if (team[i]["social"]){ %>
              <a class="about-social-icon <%= team[i]["socialid"]%>" href="<%= team[i]["social"]%>" target="_blank">
                 <i class="fa fa-<%= team[i]["socialid"] %>" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              </a>



            <% } else { }%>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</div> <!--end container -->

    <% include ../partials/footer.ejs %>
  <script src="/js/mixitup.min.js"></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/about.js"></script>

  <script>var mixer = mixitup('#team-photos');</script>
</body>
</html>
